-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">清澈得令人悲伤</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">ka na shi i ku ra i ni</span></p><p begin="03:44.374" end="03:51.450" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L58"><span begin="03:44.374" end="03:46.033">Ah-</span> <span begin="03:46.233" end="03:46.582">腕</span><span begin="03:46.582" end="03:46.918">を</span><span begin="03:46.918" end="03:47.089">伸</span><span begin="03:47.089" end="03:47.244">ば</span><span begin="03:47.244" end="03:47.594">し</span><span begin="03:47.594" end="03:47.774">て</span><span begin="03:47.774" end="03:47.946">も</span><span begin="03:47.946" end="03:48.446">届</span><span begin="03:48.446" end="03:48.626">か</span><span begin="03:48.626" end="03:48.772">な</span><span begin="03:48.772" end="03:48.940">い</span><span begin="03:48.940" end="03:49.086">よ</span><span begin="03:49.086" end="03:49.467">数</span><span begin="03:49.467" end="03:49.811">セン</span><span begin="03:49.811" end="03:49.975">チ</span><span begin="03:49.975" end="03:50.144">で</span><span begin="03:50.144" end="03:51.450">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">啊啊 哪怕伸出的手只差几厘米就能碰到</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ah- u de wo no ba shi te mo to do ka na i yo su u se n chi de mo</span></p><p begin="03:51.655" end="03:55.056" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L59"><span begin="03:51.655" end="03:51.993">最</span><span begin="03:51.993" end="03:52.344">初</span><span begin="03:52.344" end="03:52.550">か</span><span begin="03:52.550" end="03:52.710">ら</span><span begin="03:52.710" end="03:53.024">全</span><span begin="03:53.024" end="03:53.386">然</span><span begin="03:53.386" end="03:53.724">違</span><span begin="03:53.724" end="03:53.917">う</span><span begin="03:53.917" end="03:54.088">も</span><span begin="03:54.088" end="03:54.415">の</span><span begin="03:54.415" end="03:54.638">だ</span><span begin="03:54.638" end="03:54.768">っ</span><span begin="03:54.768" end="03:55.056">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">然而已不再是最初的自己</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">sa 